# Screens

- Root stack in `src/app/_layout.tsx` — headers off globally (`headerShown: false`)
- Use `Redirect` for gating (see `src/app/index.tsx`)
- Book routes: `book/[id]/index`, `ideas`, `feed` — layout in `book/[id]/_layout.tsx`
- Lesson modal: `presentation: 'card'`, `animation: 'slide_from_bottom'`
- Book feed: `presentation: 'fullScreenModal'`, `slide_from_bottom`
